      "side": 1,
      "message": "It looks like this will erase the entire image, even when the updated rectangle isn\u0027t the full size of the image. So some of the pixel data provided by a prior glTexImage2D() call may be lost. Also, if not all of the mipmap levels get updated then the texture becomes incomplete.",
